{"tid":43563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［炒散］一人一件番工系事 番工已經辛苦仲要遇到你","createTime":"2016-12-17T15:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T10:49:23.000Z","uid":59307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85a7a024a669c2676ebbee86cc7f57bbd25cb317","tid":43563,"uid":59307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:00:12.000Z","msg":"今本身就好乖咁炒散啦<br />\n結果遇到個咁既蛇頭<br />\n佢話兩星期糧咪兩星期囉<br />\n到左兩個星期後<br />\n<br />\n佢話我番完工冇同佢報糧<br />\n<br />\n之後又話要等到星期五咁好啦<br />\n我都重等得起<br />\n但結果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期六</span>都未出<br />\n咁我唯有去問佢點啦<br />\n點知佢話佢都比人拖 <br />\n所以拖咪埋我糧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但拖糧都算啦<br />\n<br />\n竟然仲要係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">炒散群</span>到po埋我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全名</span>岀黎連<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">銀行戶口</span>出燃埋黎啊屌、咁冇隱私架咩<br />\n<br />\n重有上次番佢啲工佢話出200<br />\n結果出左160、問反佢點解、佢話上次電話到只係講&quot;大約&quot;出200<br />\n咁你講咩都得架啦、找淡食姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35SLP33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35SLP33.jpg&h=aa02a69e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79e7b344cafdb5a42cd2548f67234d3e67f36ca8","tid":43563,"uid":48189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"accb8f2ebfebae5b48532e934a757c1eba5ffb72","tid":43563,"uid":40350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"認真問<br />\n炒散邊到揾最多job<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8126f6a069c8c1ce18d1f5c17732ab6494ff0ec7","tid":43563,"uid":59307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"係囉 格黎線出65<br />\n佢出50<br />\n仲講到自己冇肉食咁"},{"pid":"cecd34f503fc3d97611644ef368a64b104be89bb","tid":43563,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:15:49.000Z","msg":"開佢電話啦"},{"pid":"f149ce6f6c861f1f96689f870e287e229907485b","tid":43563,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"呢啲仆街拖糧，又出少左錢<br />\n<br />\n一於推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ff7f87898e774d524d923b2455391ed005ede2","tid":43563,"uid":59307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"唔岩聽仲會踢人架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/17/233754_681c708a0b7167dc3eb846d7f16a0fe6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F17%2F233754_681c708a0b7167dc3eb846d7f16a0fe6.jpg&h=3266f3ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a6d6bd488de521126b668684991bec3a462afab","tid":43563,"uid":59307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲仆街拖糧，又出少左錢<br />\n<br />\n一於推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講極都唔肯出足<br />\n之後好難先出多20蚊<br />\n都未捉數"},{"pid":"39cec56e22c0b69e13b3d9fb7d5b443fdf7f9b99","tid":43563,"uid":59307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開佢電話啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以開電話架咩？<br />\n新黎唔識規舉"},{"pid":"da0bc3293595b3c4411c00024384231f6130bcf5","tid":43563,"uid":48189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0731340bea9ef286d54f0ec9a14e92c301078166","tid":43563,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T02:14:47.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ca4e4df6c4d105a712634868fbd65ef5bf9383a3","tid":43563,"uid":59307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:29:59.000Z","msg":"番工個陣 個經理話唔要人 叫我收工"},{"pid":"c73a3af2253e13cd745f27724fdc9f1310c3965e","tid":43563,"uid":27437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"5111 2421<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/he